name: Geekbench: Object Detection
description: Detects and classifies objects in 300x300 pixel photos (16 in single-core mode, 64 in multi-core mode) using the MobileNet v1 SSD convolutional neural network.The score is calibrated against a baseline score of 2,500 (Dell Precision 3460 with a Core i7-12700 processor) as per the Geekbench 6 Benchmark Internals.
